<div class="content">
<h4>A tag is a keyword or label that categorizes your question with other, similar questions. Using the right tags makes it easier for others to find and answer your question.</h4>
<h4>Clicking a tag will bring you to a page with all the posts under that tag.</h4>

  <% @tags.each do |tag| %>
    <li> <%= link_to tag.description, tag_path(tag) %></li>
  <% end %>
</div>
